# Student Average

This script allows you to see the average of each student , letter grade and finally it will print all the output in a file with the average of each exam

## Usage

1-Enter the number of your students
2-Enter the name of each student and his grade on each exam (exam 1,2,3)
3-This script print the result in a new file with the average of each exam

## Requirements

- Bash shell

## Script Features

- Enter number of students
- Enter the name of each stident in class
- Enter the student grade in the exams (exam 1 , exam 2 , exam 3)
- Display the average and letter grade of each student
- display the average of each exam
- All the output will be display on a file


